{
  "text": "This solution is asymptotically Poincar\u00e9 AdS 5 and after TsT (shifting along \u03be) it gives rise to an asymptotically Poincar\u00e9 Schr\u00f6dinger black brane. The TsT-transform of this black brane solution has been studied in [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] .",
  "correct_citation": {
